        {
            "id": 6260642,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉航海王競飆漲停、生技醫療股點火 尾盤翻紅小漲2點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (4) 日多空交戰，電子權值股雖陷入高檔整理，改由金融股撐盤，生技醫療、航運股各擁題材竄紅，尾盤買單急拉後，最終翻紅收在 27795.71 點，小漲 2.67 點，終場成交量 3883 億元，為波段低點，凸顯市場觀望氣氛濃厚。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6260642/l/4df82c31528a869f0e81dd998488f17f.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉航海王競飆漲停、生技醫療股點火 尾盤翻紅小漲2點。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股普遍小漲，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 小跌 1% 內，力守月線大關，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 也都在平盤上表態，其他如廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UMC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UMC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UMC-US</a>)、國巨 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2327:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2327\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2327-TW</a>) 也都有 1% 左右的漲幅。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金控族群今日異軍突起，富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)、國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>) 雙雙大漲 2% 左右，中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)、兆豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2886:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>)、玉山金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2884:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2884\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2884-TW</a>)、元大金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2885-TW</a>)、台新新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>) 漲幅至少 1% 起跳，支撐整體大盤走勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在類股方面，2025 台灣醫療科技展今天開幕，傳出捷克採購台灣 2 億<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>醫材 ，創台灣醫療展媒合最高金額，激勵生技醫療類股大漲 2.83%；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/eod/detail/BDI\">BDI 指數</a>飆 2 年來新高，散裝航運股航海王重現威風，裕民、新興、中航、四維航齊飆漲停。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今日記憶體族群依舊是交投熱點，菱生 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2369:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2369\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2369-TW</a>) 飆漲近 8%，重返月線，華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、威剛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>) 也都上漲，不過，華東 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>)、群聯 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8299-TW</a>)、力成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6239:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6239\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6239-TW</a>) 都有 2-4% 的跌幅，族群走勢兩樣情。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
